#block(inset: 8pt, radius: 4pt, stroke: 0.5pt, fill: rgb("FFFFFF"))[#strong[Action]
#v(3pt)
Decide on a very low price (\$5-\$20) for your tiny offer. Make it a number you're comfortable asking for.
